Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report_...der_data_phase(25.10)  timing_report_...der_data_phase(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_property_fastest_clock_consider_data_phase

Syntax
       timing_report_property_fastest_clock_consider_data_phase

       {true | false}

       Default : false

       Considers the data signals while determining the fastest clock arriving
       on any given pin.

       When set to false, the clocks arriving in clock phase form will be con-
       sidered.

       When  set  to  true, the clocks arriving in clock phase as well as data
       phase form will be considered for determining the fastest clock.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

